row.entry:
Confirms orders made under section 3 of the Local Government Services (Corporate Bodies) Act 1971 in relation to bodies established under that Act. The existing corporate bodies concerned are:

   Local Government Computer Services Board;

   Dublin Transportation Office;

   Local Government Management Services Board;

   Affordable Homes Partnership;

   Irish Water Safety;

   Limerick Northside Regeneration Agency;

  Limerick Southside Regeneration Agency.
